title: Songs in A Minor - Boylove music by Elijah Wood
description:
Hi All,

I used to be an Admin of Boylover.net. While I was there, I found a collection of boylove songs by a guy called Elijah Wood on another site owned by a person called NukeSheep. 

NukeSheep's site eventually disappeared, but not before I'd had the chance to download the songs myself.

Eventually, after not hearing anything from either NukeSheep or the singer Elijah Wood, I decided to upload them to BoyLover.net where they proved to be very popular. Shortly afterwards, I was contacted by Elijah Wood, who, far from being annoyed, was happy that I still had the songs as he had not only lost his copies, but also his singing ability as a complication of surgery he had undergone.

Over the interveneing years since the closure of BoyLover.net and my own incarceration, I have managed to hang onto these songs, so I thought I would upload them here for others to enjoy.

Enjoy!



Cheers,

Ganymede
